title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open the report.
2. Export the data from a table that contains a highlight or map.

OB: N/A

EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.

SR: 
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to a table that contains a highlight or map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe if an exception is thrown (ReportEngineService.getMetaData()) when exporting the data.
